        {
          "type": "frame",
          "id": "U0PsQo",
          "name": "Section-RepoRow",
          "context": "<!--\n## Section-RepoRow\n\n**Type:** component\n**Component:** RepoRow\n\n### Purpose\nThe scrollable list row on the dashboard `/`. One row per connected repo, expandable to reveal pinned branches.\n\n### Design notes\n- 56 tall, single line, monospace for `org/repo` strings.\n- Status dot 8px on the left. Workspace chip on the right.\n- Hover reveals Open / Re-sync / Pin icon buttons.\n- Expanded variant slots BranchRow children + OtherBranchesExpander beneath inside the same group.\n\n### For AI agents\n- Variants: default-personal, default-team, hover, expanded, syncing, failed, stale.\n- Status dot colors: synced $tag-success-ink, failed $tag-danger-ink, syncing ring $color-text-secondary, stale ring $color-text-tertiary. Surface stays neutral across all states — let the dot carry the semantic.\n-->",
          "width": "fill_container",
          "fill": "#ffffff",
          "cornerRadius": 16,
          "stroke": {
            "align": "inside",
            "thickness": 1,
            "fill": "#dfe0e7"
          },
          "layout": "vertical",
          "gap": 16,
          "padding": 24,
