        {
          "type": "frame",
          "id": "KJinn",
          "layoutPosition": "absolute",
          "x": -9999,
          "y": -9999,
          "name": "DashboardTopBar-final",
          "context": "<!--\n## DashboardTopBar-final\n\n**Type:** component\n**Variant:** default\n**Component:** DashboardTopBar\n\n### Purpose\nPersistent top bar across /, /connect, and /[workspace]/[repo]/[branch]. Provides workspace switching, global search, primary 'Connect new repo' action, and the user avatar.\n\n### Design notes\n- 64px tall, 1440 wide. White surface with #dfe0e7 bottom hairline only.\n- Workspace switcher mirrors Sidebar-Header (8zJLA): dark mono initial avatar, two-line meta, chevrons-up-down trigger.\n- Search input mirrors Sidebar-Search-Bar (XlkGy): 32px tall, 1px #dfe0e7 border, lucide search icon, mono placeholder for fuzzy repo lookups.\n- Primary action (#121111 fill, white label, radius 14) is `+ Connect new repo` per build plan line 132.\n- Avatar 32px, dark fill, mono initial.\n- Reusable so all dashboard layouts share the same bar.\n\n### For AI agents\n- Override `WorkspaceSwitcher-name` text via descendants to switch contexts.\n- Override `Connect-Label` for variants like 'Connect first repo' on the empty state.\n- The bar itself never changes structurally between layouts — only inner copy.\n-->",
          "reusable": true,
          "width": 1440,
          "height": 64,
          "fill": "#ffffffff",
          "stroke": {
            "align": "inside",
            "thickness": {
              "bottom": 1
            },
            "fill": "#dfe0e7"
          },
          "padding": [
            0,
            16
          ],
          "justifyContent": "space_between",
          "alignItems": "center",
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "frame",
              "id": "avrFi",
              "name": "TopBar-Left",
              "gap": 12,
              "alignItems": "center",
              "children": [
                {
                  "type": "frame",
                  "id": "dNgvk",
                  "name": "TopBar-Brand",
                  "width": 28,
                  "height": 28,
                  "fill": "#121111ff",
