            {
              "type": "frame",
              "id": "iC6rE",
              "name": "Dashboard-expanded-final",
              "context": "<!--\n## Dashboard-expanded-final\n\n**Type:** layout\n**Variant:** expanded + popover-open\n**Component:** Dashboard\n\n### Purpose\nShows two interactions stacked on the populated dashboard at once: (a) one repo row expanded so its pinned branches are visible inline, and (b) a workspace popover open after clicking a team chip on a different row (build plan lines 158–172).\n\n### Design notes\n- Branch rows are 48px tall and indented 32px from row left to make the hierarchy obvious without nesting cards.\n- Pinned branches show a filled lucide `pin` icon (#121111). Unpinned would be ghost icon revealed on hover only.\n- 'Other branches…' expander lazy-loads from GitHub on click (build plan line 170).\n- WorkspacePopover-final is an anchored panel: 280 wide, white surface, 1px #dfe0e7, radius 12, soft shadow. It floats absolute-positioned above the row below the chip.\n- Branch row meta uses Geist Mono 12 #6d6467 for SHA + relative timestamp; status dot uses the same kit as RepoRow.\n\n### For AI agents\n- Sibling layouts: Dashboard-empty-final, Dashboard-populated-final.\n- Branch row component variants live in the kit (BranchRow-default-final, BranchRow-syncing-final, BranchRow-pinned-final, BranchRow-failed-final, BranchRow-stale-final).\n- WorkspacePopover-final lives in the kit; this layout instances it with the 'Acme' workspace.\n-->",
