                  "layout": "vertical",
                  "children": [
                    {
                      "type": "frame",
                      "id": "Po2yn",
                      "name": "InstanceBreadcrumb-default-final-anchor",
                      "context": "<!-- ## InstanceBreadcrumb-default-final\n**Type:** component\n**Variant:** default (closed branch dropdown)\n**Component:** InstanceBreadcrumb\n### Design notes\n- Mono workspace + repo + branch trigger. Branch trigger has subtle #f6f6f9 fill to telegraph it's clickable.\n- Lucide chevron-right separators @12px #9b9295.\n### For AI agents\n- Open variant lives in the component kit (InstanceBreadcrumb-branch-dropdown-open-final).\n- Build-plan-line 176: this is the only structural change to the AppShell sidebar.\n-->",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "gap": 6,
                      "padding": [
                        12,
