                      "context": "<!-- ## FeaturedRepos-Section-IterationA\n**Type:** component\n**Variant:** Iteration A canonical\n**Component:** FeaturedReposSection\n### Design notes\n- Hero card section above the all-repos list. 3 cards × ~418 wide, gap 12.\n- Section header (calm): title + 'Last 7 days' meta on left, 'View all activity' link on right.\n### For AI agents\n- Do NOT promote this above the topbar — it must sit inside the same scroll surface as the all-repos list so users see both without page jumps.\n-->",
