                          "context": "<!--\n## FeaturedRepoCard-default-final\n**Type:** state\n**Variant:** default (synced)\n**Component:** FeaturedRepoCard (Iteration A)\n### Design notes\n- White surface, radius 16, 1px #dfe0e7. Header padding [16,16,12,16], footer padding [12,16] with 1px top divider.\n- Mono `org/repo` Geist Mono 14 #121111. Meta Geist 12 #6d6467 mono for relative timestamps.\n- StatusChip top-right uses StatusDot + Geist 11 mono label.\n- Footer left: component count (Geist 12 #6d6467 mono). Footer right: 'Open' pill (radius 14, padding [0,12], height 28, dark fill).\n### For AI agents\n- This is Iteration A. Sibling iterations (B/C/D) live in FeaturedRepoCard-iterations-final.\n- Card height varies with content but should not exceed ~180px without explicit user direction.\n-->",
