                          "context": "<!--\n## FeaturedRepoCard-metrics-final\n**Type:** state\n**Variant:** Iteration C (metrics-led)\n**Component:** FeaturedRepoCard\n### Design notes\n- Same outer chrome as Iteration A, but the body emphasises a single big metric (component count) plus a tiny meta strip of secondary numbers (branches, last sync).\n- Useful when comparing scale across repos; weakest when last commit / activity matters.\n-->",
